# xarray-behave

Install a working conda installation (see [here](https://docs.conda.io/en/latest/miniconda.html)). 

```shell
conda create -c conda-forge -c ncb -n xb python=3.12 xarray-behave
```

See `demo.ipynb` for usage examples.

